---
/**
 * Mission — clean statement section
 */
---

<section class="container py-16">
  <div class="mission" data-animate>
    <header class="section-head">
      <p class="section-head__eyebrow">Our belief</p>
    </header>
      <p class="mission__text">
      We believe great software, sharp marketing and reliable IT should feel like one team — yours. Most agencies handle one piece. We handle all three, so every product, campaign and system pushes the same business forward. No handoffs, no finger-pointing, no gaps.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .mission__text {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.75rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
    margin: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
